===Noun===
'''ferroalloy'''
# any [[alloy]] of [[iron]] and another [[metal]], especially one of [[silicon]], [[manganese]], [[chromium]], [[vanadium]], [[tungsten]], [[titanium]] and [[molybdenum]]; used in the production of [[specialist]] [[steel]]s as they have a lower [[melting point]] than the pure metal

